ence or equivalent experience is required.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Working place: </strong>8th Floor - E.TOWN III - Cong Hoa Street - Tan Binh District - Ho Chi Minh City\r\n\r\nHồ sơ gửi về <strong>phuoc.nguyen@donghocat.vn</strong> hoặc <strong>quangphuoc@gmail.com</strong>\r\n\r\nLiên hệ : Mr Phước. Tel: <strong>0977 312 887</strong>', 'Automation Test - SmartOSC', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'automation-test-smartosc', '', '', '2015-03-18 20:29:15', '2015-03-18 13:29:15', '', 0, 'http://kungfuphp.com/?p=725', 0, 'post', '', 0);
